  "title": "轨道电梯：搭出电梯",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "elevator",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/sci-fi/sf-06.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "轨道电梯停在半空。只有把三块发光踏板接起来，大家才能到达高处。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是轨道电梯。我们先把“搭出电梯”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到光核在轻轻嗡鸣，信号就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先看清蓝色航线，再做一个安全的小动作。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "build",
          "prompt": "把发光踏板搭成一条安全的上升路线。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "center",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "连接蓝色踏板",
              "feedback": "踏板咔哒一声接好了。"
            },
            {
              "label": "安装黄色扶手",
              "feedback": "扶手亮起，大家走得更安心。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，连接蓝色踏板让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "扫描光点后，隐藏的星尘轨迹露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条轨迹和星图接起来，下一站就会亮起。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这束光，它会带我们穿过下一段星际航线。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "路是大家一起搭出来的，电梯又开动了。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "center"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
